===Vliegvelden verlopen niet===
{{nl/Kenmerken|1.0|align="right"|text=(1.0.0)}}
Airports may have an expiry year, similar to engines. Expired airports can't be built any more. With this option enabled, airports never expire.

This option has been renamed from [[#always-allow-small-airports|Always allow small airports]] in r16614.
:''Mogelijke instellingen:'' <span style="color:green">'''Aan'''</span> of <span style="color:red">'''Uit'''</span>
:''In Openttd.cfg config file:'' ([station] never_expire_airports = <true|false>)
{{en/-}}

===Aanpassen van de hoogte van de randen van de kaart toestaan===
{{nl/Kenmerken|0.7|align="right"|text=(0.7.0)}}
With this enabled, the map doesn't require to have water all around it and allows you to terraform the map's edges just as any place elsewhere. Selecting this feature also provides an extra set of buttons in the [[en/Archive/Manual/Terra Genesis Perlin|map generator]] to select the type of egde (water/freeform) for each side of the map.
:''Mogelijke instellingen:'' <span style="color:green">'''Aan'''</span> of <span style="color:red">'''Uit'''</span>
:''In Openttd.cfg config file:'' ([construction] freeform_edges = <true|false>)
{{en/-}}
===Plaatsing van bomen in het spel===
{{nl/Kenmerken|1.0|align="right"|text=(1.0.0)}}
With this option, you can enable/disable the in-game generation of trees.
:''Mogelijke instellingen:'' <span style="color:red">'''none''' (breaks lumber mill)</span>, <span style="color:#00693E">'''only in rain forests'''</span> or <span style="color:#00693E">'''everywhere'''</span>
:''In Openttd.cfg config file:'' ([construction] extra_tree_placement = <0-2>)
{{en/-}}
===Toestaan wanneer gepauzeerd===
{{nl/Kenmerken|1.1|align="right"|text=(1.1.1)}}
Met deze optie kun je aangeven welke mogelijkheden tijdens een spelpauze toegelaten zijn.
:''Mogelijke instellingen:'' <span style="color:red">'''none''' (breaks lumber mill)</span>, <span style="color:#00693E">'''only in rain forests'''</span> or <span style="color:#00693E">'''everywhere'''</span>
:''In Openttd.cfg config file:'' 
{{en/-}}

